+# Pala World Standards Atlas
 
-Pala OS V6 turns the V5 world-standard tabur into a machine-readable policy engine.
+Pala OS Command Center groups the 60 world standards into user-facing control areas. The product posture is simple: the world writes agents; Pala OS controls agent work with evidence, standards, risk, and owner decision.
 
 ## Status vocabulary
 - `required`: must have evidence to avoid a blocked state.
